                     <interp inst="t18200217-138-person1345" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I make handles for surgical instruments. I saw these things at Baker's shop, my wife bought them.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18200217-138-person1346">
                  JOHN 
                  MILLIKIN
               <interp inst="t18200217-138-person1346" type="surname" value="MILLIKIN"></interp>
